	NPCType Harvester_Cyclops_Infused_Heat Harvester_Cyclops_Infused_Heat
	NPCType Harvester_Cyclops_Infused_Crush Harvester_Cyclops_Infused_Crush
	NPCType Harvester_Cyclops_Shielded Harvester_Cyclops_Shielded
